
.grid_16
	%h2 Synch with your GitHub Account

	%p You can find your GitHub username by looking at the url for your profile. Or just what username you use to login.
	= image_tag "git_hub_find_id.png"
	%p Just go to GitHub, find your id, and enter it here. We can then synch your GitHub profile with your account.
		
	= form_for [:my, @git_hub_profile] do |f|
		.label= f.label :username, "GitHub username"
		.control= f.text_field :username
		.submit= f.submit "Synch", :disable_with => "Synching..."
	
.clear